segments.text: Y'all must have all been kinfolks in those days.

Did you raise many, uh, did the white folks, the poor white trash and the colored folks have many fights back in the, after the good break up?
No, we never had nothing to run into.
Well, I mean, did they have many, you know, quarrels and fights, isn't there?
No, they didn't have these white, these buyers that had killed our white, our boys, my husband and his brother.
